Welcome to Termux!

 * Search packages:   pkg search <query>
 * Use root env:      termux-chroot

USEFUL CMD
  nmap <URL>  :scan the prot at the url
  hydra       :brute force ssh/mysql
  exiftool <FILE_FULLNAME> :watch/change file meta-data
  whatportis <PORT> :check prot used to do what
  cd XSStrike/python xsstrike.py :xss check
  nginx       :start nginx server using root

